        <mxCell id="subtitle" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=12;fontColor=#666666;" value="Alarm fires → auto-collect evidence → AI analysis + triage → notebook (always written) → notify only if actionable → engineer edits / exports.   Boxes = stages;  cards beside them = detail.   v0.2 · 2026-07-05" vertex="1">
