        <mxCell id="sa4" edge="1" parent="1" source="s4" style="endArrow=block;html=1;strokeWidth=3;strokeColor=#444444;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;" target="s5">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="sa5" edge="1" parent="1" source="s5" style="endArrow=block;html=1;strokeWidth=3;strokeColor=#444444;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;" target="s6">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n1" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#fbfbf3;strokeColor=#c9c9a8;dashed=1;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;fontColor=#555555;" value="Alertmanager first-class + generic envelope (Grafana / Datadog / NR).&#xa;Intake adapter normalizes → generic alert.&#xa;Per-source auth: shared token / HMAC." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="104" width="470" x="800" y="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n2" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#fbfbf3;strokeColor=#c9c9a8;dashed=1;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;fontColor=#555555;" value="Deterministic, no AI — kills the bulk of noise cheaply.&#xa;severity ≥ high · dedup / correlate · flapping rate-limit · maintenance window.&#xa;→ ONE incident + thin entity bag (service / host / pod / env)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="104" width="470" x="800" y="228" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n3" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#fbfbf3;strokeColor=#c9c9a8;dashed=1;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;fontColor=#555555;" value="Config-bound roles · read-only · best-effort · self-describing; failure = honest gap.&#xa;metrics → Prometheus (covers Thanos / Mimir / VictoriaMetrics / SigNoz)&#xa;logs → Loki | Elasticsearch (pluggable) · dashboards → Grafana panel snapshots&#xa;orchestrator → Kubernetes (optional)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="104" width="470" x="800" y="356" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n4" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#fbfbf3;strokeColor=#c9c9a8;dashed=1;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;fontColor=#555555;" value="Pluggable provider — Anthropic ⟷ OpenAI-compat, incl. internal vLLM / Ollama / gateway; evidence never leaves the network.&#xa;Output: summary · timeline · ranked hypotheses (every claim cites evidence) · evidence gaps · TRIAGE VERDICT (actionable?)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="104" width="470" x="800" y="484" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n5" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#fbfbf3;strokeColor=#c9c9a8;dashed=1;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;fontColor=#555555;" value="PostgreSQL — JSONB document + indexed columns + full-text search; panel PNGs on disk, referenced from DB.&#xa;ALWAYS WRITTEN — evidence survives even if AI analysis fails.&#xa;Evidence = immutable audit trail." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="104" width="470" x="800" y="612" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="n6" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#fbfbf3;strokeColor=#c9c9a8;dashed=1;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;fontColor=#555555;" value="Notification GATE: actionable → page / Slack; likely-noise → quiet / digest (filter the NOTIFY, never the record).&#xa;Channels: Slack first, pluggable — carries the ANALYSIS. Web notebook: list · search · timeline · evidence · hypotheses · resolution.&#xa;Export: DOCX · PDF · Markdown · JSON — generated on demand, NOT stored." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="104" width="470" x="800" y="740" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="cfg" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;spacingRight=8;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=11;" value="valaf.yaml — dynamic role binding&#xa;&#xa;one active binding per role · unconfigured role = honest gap · dormant adapters cost nothing.&#xa;intake · collectors (metrics / logs / dashboards / orchestrator) · analysis (anthropic | openai-compat)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="150" width="350" x="40" y="120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="learn" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;spacingRight=8;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;" value="Learning loop — retrieval, not training&#xa;&#xa;find_similar() → past RESOLVED incidents w/ overlapping alerts:&#xa;verified root causes + ruled-out hypotheses → rendered into the prompt." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="350" x="40" y="486" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ec" edge="1" parent="1" source="cfg" style="endArrow=open;html=1;dashed=1;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#999999;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;exitX=1;exitY=0.25;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;" target="s1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="el" edge="1" parent="1" source="learn" style="endArrow=block;html=1;dashed=1;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#d79b00;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;" target="s4">
